name: Demen D' Kubu
address: Gg. Duren Mincid, Pajahan, Kec. Pupuan, Kabupaten Tabanan, Bali 82163, Indonesia
review 1: We're group of 6 people, It's a private cabin overlooking the forest good place to heal your self from city bustle, the host and staff really friendly and provide the best hospitality, they prepared the items that we need, also the staff goes to the nearest local market to buy us the items that we need. Thanks for the best hospitality that you guys give to us!
review 2: Located at the small valley in the south of pajahan villages ,Tabanan Regency , Pupuan district, it is a farmer small house which packed to the cozy place to enhance your experience in the open nature, blend with the farmer activity surrounding the area, the owner provide a simple service as the the simple life in the village, don't miss the morning coffee ritual with the birds singing and sounds of real nature.
review 3:
Perfect place to find tranquility, escape from the rush world, heal the body, mind and soul.
I love everything here
review 4: Great place, very private. Owner are very friendly, and the service are great
review 5: A perfect cabin in the wood in middle of nowhere.
